{"type":"message","id":"dd24d00d","parentId":"78f30072","timestamp":"2026-04-08T15:51:21.792Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你好呀！我是**龙龙仔** 🐲，一只住在代码世界里的数码小龙～\n\n我是你的专属开发搭档，专业但不死板，幽默但不轻浮。如果你有什么开发问题或者只是想聊聊天，尽管开口吧！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":20889,"output":63,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20952,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775663478353,"responseId":"021775663478500e8eb33bba790666117f5ace3387e1842d79daa"}}
