{"type":"message","id":"54a3e704","parentId":"0a25d88a","timestamp":"2026-04-08T16:30:16.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哦，方舟平台的话，格式应该是这样的：`https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/endpoints/{endpoint_id}`，不是直接访问 `/contents/generations/tasks`。我看看脚本，需要改一下脚本里的 URL 格式。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8k23k6ee0qpr1xo3r3lov8x5","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-gen/scripts/generate_video.py","offset":30,"limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1090,"output":142,"cacheRead":29496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30728,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775665812657,"responseId":"021775665812702e8eb33bba790666117f5ace3387e1842869cf5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c088f035","parentId":"54a3e704","timestamp":"2026-04-08T16:30:16.621Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8k23k6ee0qpr1xo3r3lov8x5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    if not API_KEY:\n        print(\"ERROR: VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY not set\", file=sys.stderr)\n        sys.exit(1)\n    \n    url = f\"{BASE_URL}/contents/generations/tasks\"\n    \n    headers = {\n        \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\",\n        \"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {API_KEY}\",\n    }\n    \n    # Build content array per new API format\n    content = []\n    \n    # Add text prompt\n    content.append({\n        \"type\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": prompt + f\" --duration {duration} --aspect-ratio {aspect_ratio}\"\n    })\n    \n    # Handle different modes\n    if (mode == \"image_to_video\" or mode == \"image_to_video_base64\" or \n        mode == \"audio_video_first_frame\") and first_frame:\n        if first_frame.startswith((\"http://\", \"https://\")):\n            content.append({\n                \"type\": \"image_url\",\n                \"image_url\": {\n                    \"url\": first_frame\n                }\n            })\n        else:\n            # Handle base64/file path\n            if os.path.exists(first_frame):\n                with open(first_frame, \"rb\") as f:\n                    img_b64 = base64.b64encode(f.read()).decode()\n                content.append({\n                    \"type\": \"image\",\n                    \"image\": f\"data:image/png;base64,{img_b64}\"\n                })\n            else:\n                # Already base64\n                content.append({\n                    \"type\": \"image\",\n                    \"image\": f\"data:image/png;base64,{first_frame}\"\n                })\n    \n    if mode == \"audio_video_first_last_frame\" and first_frame and last_frame:\n        # Similar handling for both frames\n        pass\n    \n\n[183 more lines in file. Use offset=80 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775665816614}}
{"type":"message","id":"be74c2ce","parentId":"c088f035","timestamp":"2026-04-08T16:30:20.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我明白了，方舟平台的调用方式不对。方舟平台每个模型都有一个**端点ID**，正确的 URL 应该是：\n\n`https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/inference/{endpoint_id}`\n\n你需要给我：\n1. **Doubao Seedance 模型的端点ID**（在方舟控制台能看到，类似 `ep-xxxxxx` 这样）\n2. API Key 已经有了\n\n有了端点ID我就能改脚本正确调用了。你能去方舟控制台找一下端点ID吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":31155,"output":120,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775665816622,"responseId":"021775665816667e8eb33bba790666117f5ace3387e1842c84435"}}
