{"type":"message","id":"6cf61b99","parentId":"b82a987a","timestamp":"2026-04-08T16:43:03.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在知道了，路径是对了，但是服务端返回 500 内部错误。这说明两种可能性：\n\n1. **你的端点权限不够** —— Seedance 视频生成现在需要申请白名单，不是所有账号都能直接用\n2. **模型名称不对** —— Doubao Seedance 的模型名称就是端点 ID，不用再单独指定 model\n\n我们试试第二种情况，把 model 直接用端点 ID：\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_44khcvgp22nkeyecgsn3g8dw","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-gen/scripts/generate_video.py \"卡通风格特朗普坐在现代客厅沙发上玩手机，皱着眉头表情困惑，搞笑风格，色彩鲜艳，明亮光线，竖屏比例9:16，时长5秒\" --mode text_to_video --model ep-m-20260321230845-4fr4d --output /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/trump_iran_video.mp4","env":{"VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY":"cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400","VIDEO_GEN_BASE_URL":"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3","VIDEO_ENDPOINT_ID":"ep-m-20260321230845-4fr4d"}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":2708,"output":345,"cacheRead":43320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46373,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775666578938,"responseId":"021775666578979e8eb33bba790666117f5ace3387e184254411d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fb229456","parentId":"6cf61b99","timestamp":"2026-04-08T16:43:06.072Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_44khcvgp22nkeyecgsn3g8dw","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Creating video task: model=ep-m-20260321230845-4fr4d, mode=text_to_video\nStatus: 500\nResponse: {\"error\":{\"code\":\"InternalServiceError\",\"message\":\"The service encountered an unexpected internal error. Request id: 021775666583821289ee8f5cd43d8cc040debd1abd108aea8a2a7\",\"param\":\"\",\"type\":\"InternalServerError\"}}\nERROR: API call failed: Server error '500 Internal Server Error' for url 'https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/chat/completions'\nFor more information check: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/500\nResponse text: {\"error\":{\"code\":\"InternalServiceError\",\"message\":\"The service encountered an unexpected internal error. Request id: 021775666583821289ee8f5cd43d8cc040debd1abd108aea8a2a7\",\"param\":\"\",\"type\":\"InternalServerError\"}}\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":2426,"aggregated":"Creating video task: model=ep-m-20260321230845-4fr4d, mode=text_to_video\nStatus: 500\nResponse: {\"error\":{\"code\":\"InternalServiceError\",\"message\":\"The service encountered an unexpected internal error. Request id: 021775666583821289ee8f5cd43d8cc040debd1abd108aea8a2a7\",\"param\":\"\",\"type\":\"InternalServerError\"}}\nERROR: API call failed: Server error '500 Internal Server Error' for url 'https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/chat/completions'\nFor more information check: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/500\nResponse text: {\"error\":{\"code\":\"InternalServiceError\",\"message\":\"The service encountered an unexpected internal error. Request id: 021775666583821289ee8f5cd43d8cc040debd1abd108aea8a2a7\",\"param\":\"\",\"type\":\"InternalServerError\"}}\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775666586067}}
{"type":"message","id":"05700929","parentId":"fb229456","timestamp":"2026-04-08T16:43:12.346Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"还是 500... 看来问题不在这儿。现在能确定的是：\n\n✅ API 端点路径通了（不 404 了）  \n✅ 认证也过了（否则是 401）  \n❌ 但是服务端内部错误\n\n这说明**你的这个端点可能还没有开通 Seedance 视频生成权限**。Doubao Seedance 现在还是邀测阶段，需要申请白名单才能用。\n\n不过没关系！虽然 API 暂时没调通，但我给你的那个剪映五分制作方案真的非常简单，我们已经有完整剧本了，你打开剪映跟着做就能出来成品：\n\n---\n\n## 🎬 五分钟就能做好的完整操作\n\n1. **搜两张表情包**\n   - 百度搜「特朗普 卡通表情包」保存一张\n   - 再搜「伊朗 表情包」或者随便找个胡子大叔喝茶的图片\n\n2. **剪映操作**\n   - 打开剪映 → 开始创作 → 导入两张图片\n   - 第一张放 0-4 秒，第二张放 4-8 秒\n   - 最后 8-15 秒，把两张图拼在一起（剪映「布局」选分屏就行）\n\n3. **加字幕**（按这个顺序）\n   - 0-4秒：**川普：没人比我更懂抖音...**\n   - 4-7秒：**伊朗：哦？川总关注我了？**\n   - 7-10秒：**这是要...拼单买茶叶？**\n   - 10-15秒：**原来国际政治就是朋友圈点赞 👇 你觉得他们会互关吗？**\n\n4. **加配音**（最简单）\n   - 点「音频」→「智能配音」\n   - 粘进去：\n     ```\n     我就说，没有人比我更懂抖音！\n     怎么...给伊朗发私信还需要关注啊？\n\n     哦？川总关注我了？\n     这是要...拼单买茶叶？\n\n     原来国际政治就是朋友圈点赞啊！\n     ```\n   - 选个「搞笑方言」或者「幽默小哥」音色\n\n5. **加BGM**\n   - 音乐搜「搞笑」，选个免费的，音量调到 20% 就行\n\n6. **导出发抖音/快手**！\n\n---\n\n这样做出来效果反而比 AI 生成更好，因为你可以完全控制节奏和笑点。你觉得呢？要是你不想动手，等你确认端点权限开通了，我再帮你用 AI 生成。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1286,"output":580,"cacheRead":45368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47234,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775666586074,"responseId":"021775666586117e8eb33bba790666117f5ace3387e184251cf27"}}
